Unix build, where libtool/automake/autoconf works:

  (optional)% ./buildconf
            % ./configure --with-apache2-apxs=/path/to/apache2/bin/apxs
            % make && make test
  (optional)% make perl_glue
  (optional)% make perl_test
            % make install
  (optional)% make perl_install


Win32 build:
  C:\httpd-apreq-2> cd win32
  C:\httpd-apreq-2\win32> perl Configure.pl
  C:\httpd-apreq-2\win32> nmake
  C:\httpd-apreq-2\win32> nmake test
  C:\httpd-apreq-2\win32> nmake mod_apreq
  C:\httpd-apreq-2\win32> cd ..\glue\perl
  C:\httpd-apreq-2\glue\perl> perl Makefile.PL
  C:\httpd-apreq-2\glue\perl> nmake
  C:\httpd-apreq-2\glue\perl> nmake test
